ShadowBox - Class in shadows
Represents the 3D cuboidal area of the world in which objects will cast shadows (basically represents the orthographic projection area for the shadow render pass).
ShadowBox(Matrix4f, Camera) - Constructor for class shadows.ShadowBox
Creates a new shadow box and calculates some initial values relating to the camera's view frustum, namely the width and height of the near plane and (possibly adjusted) far plane.
ShadowFrameBuffer - Class in shadows
The frame buffer for the shadow pass.
ShadowFrameBuffer(int, int) - Constructor for class shadows.ShadowFrameBuffer
Initialises the frame buffer and shadow map of a certain size.
